	<div class="wrapper">
		
					
		<h2 class='flexible-html-title flexible-title'>		GENERAL TERMS OF SALE		</h2>
				
		<div class="flexible-html-content post-content"><div class='col-row auto-height-wrapper'><div class='col-half'></p>
<p>Prices indicated include VAT at the rate set by applicable regulations for transport services (*), driver service, fuel and unlimited insurance for passengers; tolls, parking fees and meals are to be paid by the passengers.</p>
<p>Each passenger may have up to 30 kg of luggage. The luggage remains their responsibility.</p>
<p>On request, a transport document may be issued to the passenger after the transport service.</p>
<p>Accepted methods of payment: Cash, cheques, bank cards (Visa, American Express, Master Card, etc.).</p>
<p>All transport services must be paid upon completion of the service; if the passenger has an account with us, the service will be paid upon receipt of invoice, before the 15th of the month following the service.</p>
<p>Any complaints must be made within eight days of the transport service.</p>
<p>Disputes will be settled by the courts of law in the place of the head office of CHABÉ Limousines.</p>
<p></div></p>
<p><div class='col-half'></p>
<p>The paid transport of passengers is a regulated business. Only authorised vehicles (VTC, occasional transport) can carry out this service.</p>
