<div  class="flexible-layout flexible-html theme-white" style="padding:40px 0 50px 0;"
		>
		
	<div class="wrapper">
		
					
		<h2 class='flexible-html-title flexible-title'>		FAQ		</h2>
				
		<div class="flexible-html-content post-content"><div class='col-row auto-height-wrapper'><div class='col-half'></p>
<p><strong>1. IS CHABÉ AUTHORISED TO TRANSPORT PEOPLE AND DOES IT HAVE THE CORRECT INSURANCES?</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>The chauffeur-driven transport business is strictly controlled. All companies in the CHABÉ group are registered on the ATOUT France register and all have a transport license per coach. All of our drivers have a special licence.</p>
<p>The shuttle transport business in vehicles with more than 9 seats is also regulated. SERVICE AFFAIRES, which sells this service, is licensed to use a passenger coach. All of our drivers have the D-category driver’s license and the FIMO (LGV) license.</p>
<p>CHABÉ has all the necessary and specific insurances for this activity and manages all risks related to its transport business.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>2. WHO ARE CHABÉ’S REFERENCES?</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>One of CHABÉ’s values is confidentiality. We do not provide information on our customers.</p>
<p>As a leader in chauffeur-driven transport for over 90 years, CHABÉ has developed a high reputation among private, public, national and international customers.</p>
<p>As a leader in long-term transport services, SERVICE AFFAIRES has commercial links and relationships with the majority of CAC 40 companies, with government institutions and the liberal professions.</p>
<p></div></p>
<p><div class='col-half'></p>
<p><strong>3. HOW MANY DRIVERS DOES CHABÉ HAVE? WHAT IS THEIR STATUS?</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>CHABÉ has over 250 drivers on open-ended contracts, for reasons of quality.</p>
<p>CHABÉ is not a temporary agency for drivers: all of our transport services are designed with optimal quality in mind and we only use limited numbers of sub-contractors.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>4. IS IT POSSIBLE TO HIRE A CAR WITHOUT A DRIVER?</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Non, il s’agit là d’une activité de location, que CHABÉ ne pratique pas.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>5. EST-IL POSSIBLE DE BÉNÉFICIER D’UN SERVICE DE CHAUFFEUR SANS LA VOITURE?</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>No. CHABÉ is not a rental agency.</p>
<p></div></p>
<p></div>
